    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or use. Mechanically, it is in perfect working order with a complete service history and has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom-quality condition, perfect for a discerning collector or someone who demands the very best.",
